The first virtual operator will reach the Czech Republic since this year.
Maybe
Perhaps the mobile telephony market in the Czech Republic is mature enough and our operators offer virtually all the services as their partners in Western Europe.
However, something is missing – a virtual operator that forces traditional ones to lower the price.
