"The expansion of this success project is being discussed, but in the Czech Republic the negotiations have little expectations.
Mobilking's ignition will take place rather in the other countries of our area," said Jana Studničková, the spokesman for the Penta Financial Group's press, in a phone dialogue.
It thus indirectly confirmed that the current operators in the Czech Republic are certainly not very favourable to this idea.
On the contrary, they try to do everything they can to prevent any competitive potential being created.
For a while he is not hiding his interest in starting a virtual operator, the GTS Novera group that would like to take another step to become a real competitor of Telefónika O2 in the field of business customers.
