So maybe there'll be better times.
Unofficial information indicates that the first virtual operator should have it by the end of the year.
For now, however, around its creation there is an impenetrable wall of silence.
"At this point, we do not believe that there is room in the Czech market for the creation of a fully-fledged virtual operator.
The Czech market, unlike other markets, is very specific.
So far no subject with a complex and serious project has addressed us," he mentioned in his statement to Mobil.cz Vlastimil Sršeň of the press section of Telefónika O2.
Other operators also use the specificities of the Czech market.
The press spokesman for T-Mobile Martina Kemrová adds in a rare agreement with the statement O2: "For now we have not noticed any vital and beneficial commercial project for both, on which it is possible to continue to build".
